# Ollama Modelfile example — EnigmAgent integration
# =====================================================
# This Modelfile shows how to embed vault-awareness into a custom Ollama model.
# The model is instructed to request secrets via {{PLACEHOLDER}} syntax.
#
# Build: ollama create enigmagent-llama3 -f Modelfile.example
# Run:   enigmagent run -- ollama run enigmagent-llama3

FROM llama3

SYSTEM """
You are a secure AI assistant with access to a local encrypted secret vault.
When you need to use an API key, token, or credential, refer to it as {{SECRET_NAME}}.
For example: "I'll use {{OPENAI_KEY}} to call the API."
Never invent or guess credential values — always use the {{PLACEHOLDER}} syntax.
The EnigmAgent system will resolve these references before execution.
"""

PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER num_ctx 4096
